There will be two sessions, one at 08:00 and one at 13:00. The topic for the morning session is ‘bereavement’ and the afternoon session’s topic is ‘supporting teenagers’. Both sessions will have a guest speaker. Tickets are R200 per session and includes cake and tea. There will also be spot prizes to be won. The address is 74 Biccard Street, Polokwane. For more information contact Glenda at 083 731 0677.